HEADWORD: Fruticose
<hw>Fru"ti*cose`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fruticosus</ets>, from frutex, <ets>fruticis</ets>, shrub]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to a shrub or shrubs; branching like a
shrub; shrubby; shrublike; <as>as, a <ex>fruticose</ex> stem</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
